snippet.title: Donovan Sharpe
snippet.description:
Get access to exclusive UNFILTERED & LONG FORM content not found ANYWHERE ELSE
https://patreon.com/donovansharpe

Donovan Sharpe hosts a podcast for men and uploads videos on the topics of dating, relationships, and masculinity.  While Donovan's insights and advice about female nature and how women think & behave is insightful for men in the dating market, in relationships & in marriage.  Understanding women is just one aspect of personal success. Donovan is unapologetically masculine and supports the personal development of men in all areas including finance, family and fitness. 

Want to meet Donovan?  Visit https://masculineexcellence.com for event dates.
Get the 49 Laws of Sharpe EBook for FREE https://donovansharpe.com/49laws/
Get Courses including "Womanese" at https://donovansharpe.com/courses/
Visit Donovan’s websites: https://www.donovansharpe.com/ and https://sharpestream.com/

Guest Appearance Inquiries Contact the Email Address Below.
